    "description": "<p>CE-Test &amp; Measurement (S) Pte Ltd (“CETM”) was incorporated in Singapore on 28 June 1989. Our core business then was to cater to the demands for high quality electronic test and measuring equipment with the rapidly growing electronic manufacturing business environment in the 90s.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We have since progress and built an extensive range of test and measuring product line to meet our customer’s demanding needs and applications. Our team grew to expand our market coverage of key industries like electrical manufacturing, utilities, education, transportation, oil &amp; gas, marine shipbuilding and more.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Moving forward, we have also expanded our global presence with offices in Malaysia, Indonesia and Vietnam. With a team of more than 60 experienced and professional employees fully committed to the goals and visions of CETM, we are ready to take CETM to a next level.</p>",
